components.templateData:
<mat-form-field appearance="fill" class="example-form-field">
    <mat-label>Enter a date range</mat-label>
    <mat-date-range-input [rangePicker]="rangePicker">
        <input matStartDate placeholder="Start date">
        <input matEndDate placeholder="End date">
    </mat-date-range-input>
    <mat-datepicker-toggle matSuffix [for]="rangePicker"></mat-datepicker-toggle>
    <mat-date-range-picker #rangePicker>
        <mat-date-range-picker-actions>
            <button mat-button matDateRangePickerCancel>Cancel</button>
            <button mat-raised-button color="primary" matDateRangePickerApply>Apply</button>
        </mat-date-range-picker-actions>
    </mat-date-range-picker>
</mat-form-field>

components.name: IonMenuComponent
components.templateData:
<ion-menu side="start" menuId="custom" contentId="main" class="my-custom-menu">
    <ion-header>
        <ion-toolbar color="tertiary">
            <ion-buttons slot="start">
                <ion-menu-button></ion-menu-button>
            </ion-buttons>
            <ion-title>Custom Menu</ion-title>
        </ion-toolbar>
    </ion-header>
    <ion-content>

        <ion-list>
            <ion-menu-toggle auto-hide="false">
                <ion-item>Menu Item</ion-item>
                <ion-item>Menu Item</ion-item>
                <ion-item>Menu Item</ion-item>
                <ion-item>Menu Item</ion-item>
                <ion-item>Menu Item</ion-item>
            </ion-menu-toggle>
        </ion-list>
    </ion-content>
</ion-menu>
<ion-router-outlet id="main" main></ion-router-outlet>

components.name: RadioButtonComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-radio-group class="example-radio-group" aria-label="Select an option">
    <label id="radio-button-label">{{radioButtonsLabel}}</label>
    <mat-radio-button class="example-radio-button" [color]="color" [disabled]="disabled" *ngFor="let label of labels" [value]="label">{{ label }}</mat-radio-button>

</mat-radio-group>

components.name: SelectComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-form-field appearance="fill">
    <mat-label>{{label}}</mat-label>
    <ng-template [ngIf]="requiredSelection ==false">
        <mat-select>
            <mat-option *ngFor="let option of options" [value]="option.value">
                {{option.viewValue}}
            </mat-option>
        </mat-select>
    </ng-template>
    <ng-template [ngIf]="requiredSelection">
        <mat-select matNativeControl required>
            <mat-option *ngFor="let option of options" [value]="option.value">{{option.viewValue}}</mat-option>
        </mat-select>
    </ng-template>
</mat-form-field>
